{"id": "1479475299237494888", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "**前排提醒：以下全是我的主观意见，你反驳就是你对，我不想吵架**\n对比很慢因为我要找资料，不完全对因为知识有限毕竟我技术也一般般\n总之非常非常主观的设计对比，我个人**几乎完全否认**新立绘，不扯专业方面单从立绘的气质和看起来舒不舒服我也觉得需要回调", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T13:46:38.660000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-07T13:39:42.678000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 20}, {"emoji": "🇬🇧", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1479475299769913495", "filename": "2026-03-07_004028.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3464632}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479477049772085399", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "some people may call this a concept work but you don’t get to this stage and somehow it’s still a concept", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T13:53:36.020000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479477049453314208", "filename": "IMG_1907.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 310797}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479477131678453781", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "I feel like they draw a new Arachne over old Arachne\nand it just doesn’t have her original charm", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T13:53:55.548000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479477202998530224", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "I particularly like the old eyelashes and the eyes better", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T13:54:12.552000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479478636808634398", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "首先气质，小图都能非常明显看出整个面部是完全不一样的气质\n原立绘眼型更加慵懒，因为半眯着+眼距也更宽，眼皮走向和眼睛轮廓收边看起来下垂，而且从面部阴影来看，眼睛轮廓会更加立体和成熟\n而新立绘把眼部最右边的眼部轮廓放大了，所以眼睛视角从稍微的俯视变成了几乎是平视\n\n原立绘鼻梁比较概括，所以看起来比较挺，而挺一些的鼻子通常会让角色看起来更加成熟\n新立绘则是概括的小鼻子，一般脸部刻画越幼则明显\n这就导致面部的比例几乎和缩短了一样", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T13:59:54.399000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-06T16:22:26.526000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479478635441164450", "filename": "6Q61D98QM_Z0BSEPED.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1658901}, {"id": "1479478636057723051", "filename": "05NUUN56W3K9P0YUB.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 983541}, {"id": "1479478636536008817", "filename": "FIVN833D3DWK66PJ43.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 997516}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479479760357687399", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "把图片缩小来看，阿拉克涅眼底最深的地方是下眼睑，而新立绘把最深的那部分和眼睛分很开，这几乎不是下眼睑的范围，而是脸部腮红的范围", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T14:04:22.274000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479479760064090112", "filename": "2DNLHVNISZAUZOVY2U.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 38226}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479481073984606299", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "在宣纸娘给出的概念设计中，“钢笔渗墨和拖拽痕迹“几乎贯穿了你游插图的绘画和设计理念，那么原立绘非常明显||因为众所周知它是压了好几年的稿||有着钢笔拖拽的感觉，但是新立绘更像是普遍的卡闭塞", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T14:09:35.467000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479481072772190208", "filename": "RXT7ES1EE47QLM.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1891522}, {"id": "1479481073590075564", "filename": "YOY7_KMVLUVC57Q9.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1112996}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479483850634690681", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "还有一个非常明显的地方就是脖子\n原立绘大领和新立绘收缩的小领给脖子视角呈现的也会不一样\n新立绘有种非常纤细的感觉，就是很容易捏断，而且因为歪到一边会增加一点妩媚的气质，脑袋看起来明显斜到一边，肩颈头在同一视角线上，削弱了原本的空间感\n但是对比阿拉克涅的原立绘看起来只是稍微歪了一下脖子向前倾\n\n因为领子顶到脖子的存在，旧立绘的头没有和新立绘一样，被衬托着看起来像大头娃娃", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T14:20:37.472000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-07T04:32:46.525000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479483847992414248", "filename": "E5_HIA8AGS45FQLO.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 64530}, {"id": "1479483848914895061", "filename": "LRY1JSWG0UUBTN.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 23656}, {"id": "1479483849519005726", "filename": "I7OFLHRPI6PF7ZJXO9RV.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 37522}, {"id": "1479483850072527064", "filename": "0YUUD8_UPGG7_CIAC.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 21392}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479486904411095101", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "在头发上因为新立绘多编了一个辫子（？）（没有高清图我看不清，看轮廓就好了）的存在，导致左侧长发没有很能够很柔顺地下去，视觉引导上变得狭窄\n\n右侧的刘海也是一样的问题，视觉上的蓬松感因为发尾走向不同直接被缩小\n左侧刘海则堆叠了两层，但是右侧并没有足够多的阴影达到视觉上的平衡，导致左侧刘海看起来非常重", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T14:32:45.549000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-06T14:55:46.855000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479486902808608880", "filename": "N00U8LHG2LAEXK_3I5.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 554338}, {"id": "1479486903249272982", "filename": "3G0EL4L_DYB5RSLSTM.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 163802}, {"id": "1479486903937007717", "filename": "8ABFAC_OJBEG683CH.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 240248}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479488598729424946", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且左侧刘海的无效分叉太多了，原立绘会更简一些", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T14:39:29.506000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479492530210082928", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "单从打光来看，在图画上，一般几何图形越接近三角形越舒适，因为三角形是稳定结构\n新立绘的几何图形没有那么规整，而且衣服高光部分因为左边似乎归于头发遮住衣服，让阴影也没有达到视觉平衡", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T14:55:06.844000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479492528054079529", "filename": "HKXMMUDGNC2OKJJ8T1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 643122}, {"id": "1479492528741941360", "filename": "N4C7XMXUTZUAME1EC.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 173860}, {"id": "1479492529199255622", "filename": "AFLZNQZASVXU_T1LSTV5.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 944113}, {"id": "1479492529585000570", "filename": "U6WOTJBXMIAIX0VD.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 537933}, {"id": "1479492529916346449", "filename": "2QDB2LMR468SKZVFQOA2.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 293234}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479495927298392216", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "旧立绘更像贵妇人，不是很标准的v型，视觉上把领结收束在里面，下方的白色带子也被收在衣服里，看起来气质比较比较工整和规范\n新立绘则直接是深v，凹出了胸部，带子直接改成领结放在外面，更像水手服的领结，这样显得气质更加活泼和少女\n~~还有这个新立绘把上面突出来的白色带子改的看起来和露出胸罩一样到底是何意味~~", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T15:08:36.773000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-06T15:08:52.509000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479495926593753141", "filename": "YR77OTIL5OYFI92FVI.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 126734}, {"id": "1479495926971367606", "filename": "D0SC_XQ91LS22VW_XP.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 71258}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479496606050160855", "channel_id": "1479475299237494888", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "手臂部分原立绘手臂是垂下再抬起，新立绘正面看变为了平放的样子，手臂先向前再上抬，所以动作看起来较为拘谨，没有原立绘那么放松", "timestamp": "2026-03-06T15:11:18.600000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-07T03:29:45.130000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479496605249044615", "filename": "S5UW8_FQI0NQA6PH3D0.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 267868}, {"id": "1479496605659955253", "filename": "AQJS20AY3NKG2WX.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 153964}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
